OL,3,CCyclist who broke his elbows and jaw
OL,4,Cafter being throw from bike sues
OL,5,Ccouncil
OL,7,FA cyclist who broke his elbows and jaw
OL,8,Fafter being thrown from his bike by a
OL,9,Ffeature meant to improve road safety
OL,10,Fis suing the council.
OL,12,FGreg Simmons was catapulted into the
OL,13,Froad when he hit a lane divider in
OL,14,FEdmonton. The screenwriter described
OL,15,Fhitting a large bit of plastic which
OL,16,Fhe says was hard to see.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/7
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1784117906
OL,3,CCyclist who broke his elbows and jaw
OL,4,Cafter being throw from bike sues
OL,5,Ccouncil
OL,7,FThe 36-year-old has never fully
OL,8,Frecovered from his serious injuries.
OL,9,FThe council denies the safety measure
OL,10,Fis defective but Greg fears what
OL,11,Fhappened to him could happen to
OL,12,Fsomeone else.
OL,14,F"I was cycling down Hertford Road and
OL,15,FI had to oveertake a bus that had
OL,16,Fpulled in front of me into a bus
OL,17,Fstop," Greg told ITV News London.
OL,19,FHe added: "So I pulled out inti the
OL,20,Froad but I hit a divider which is
OL,21,Falmost invisible without a bollard.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/7
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1784117906
OL,3,CCyclist who broke his elbows and jaw
OL,4,Cafter being throw from bike sues
OL,5,Ccouncil
OL,7,F"I went over the handlebars, I landed
OL,8,Fin the road, broke both my elbows and
OL,9,Fmy jaw.
OL,11,F"I got lucky because it's a busy road
OL,12,Fand I could have been hit by a car."
OL,14,FGreg claims the way the council has
OL,15,Fdesigned the cycle lane makes it
OL,16,Fdangerous.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/7
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1784117906
OL,3,CCyclist who broke his elbows and jaw
OL,4,Cafter being throw from bike sues
OL,5,Ccouncil
OL,7,FHe said: "Most of the dividers have
OL,8,Fbollards, but this one didn't - it
OL,9,Fdoesn't have a safety bollard, it
OL,10,Fdoesn't have reflectors, it doesn't
OL,11,Fhave any paint.
OL,13,F"It's very difficult to spot that as
OL,14,Fyou travel at speed."
OL,16,FGreg is currently fighting a legal
OL,17,Fcase against Enfield Council which is
OL,18,Frefusing to admit liability. The
OL,19,Fcouncil said it could not comment
OL,20,Fwhile legal proceedings were ongoing.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/7
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1784117906
OL,3,CCyclist who broke his elbows and jaw
OL,4,Cafter being throw from bike sues
OL,5,Ccouncil
OL,7,FGreg's solicitor, Sam Collard, from
OL,8,FOsbournes Law said: "From a common
OL,9,Fsense point of view it seems this is a
OL,10,Fhazard.
OL,12,F"The point of if is to keep cyclists
OL,13,Fsafe but it seems to have done the
OL,14,Fopposite.
OL,16,F"Hopefully the council will have a
OL,17,Fchange of heart and engage with us."
OL,19,FGreg's crash happened 18 months ago
OL,20,Fand while he is back on his bike he is
OL,21,Fnot fully recovered.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/7
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1784117906
OL,3,CCyclist who broke his elbows and jaw
OL,4,Cafter being throw from bike sues
OL,5,Ccouncil
OL,7,F"My left arm is not the same as it was
OL,8,Fand I don't think it ever will be,"
OL,9,FGreg said.
OL,11,F"It has lost 20 per cent muscle
OL,12,Faccording to my doctor and can't fully
OL,13,Fstraighten.
OL,15,F"It took me a while to get back on the
OL,16,Fbike but have done now, thankfully.
OL,18,F"I'll never have the same strength
OL,19,Fthat I did but I won't let that affect
OL,20,Fmy life," he explained.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/7
